Yes, it&#39;s certainly possible.  We don&#39;t know what they&#39;re really capable 
of.

In either case, it amazes me they can generate messages from programmed 
phonemes or streams of words spoken over radio broadcasts.

Zack

On Thu, 2 Oct 2008, suzanne bibb wrote:

&gt; My team has not yet purchased the Ovilus but I have been told that it has the ability to form words that have not been programmed into it.� Since I have never used one, I am wondering what are the similarities between the Ovilus and Frank&#39;s Box.� Could it be at all possible that rather than just forming words or sounds based on atmospheric readings, spirits are speaking through the Ovilus as they do Frank&#39;s box?�
&gt; �
&gt; I don&#39;t mean to sound silly or presumptous, but I am very very curious!!� I am looking forward to purchasing the Ovilus as well as the puck in the near future!� Thanks for any feedback onthe Ovilus!
&gt;
&gt;
&gt; --- On Thu, 10/2/08, Carol B. &lt;cbreck@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; From: Carol B. &lt;cbreck@...&gt;
&gt; Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] The Ovilus
&gt; To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
&gt; Date: Thursday, October 2, 2008, 1:12 PM
&gt;
&gt;
&gt;
&gt;
&gt;
