&gt; I have a puck, and I have been getting the name Seth too. I also have had
&gt; my puck give words that are not on the list.
&gt;
&gt; Carol B.
&gt;
&gt;&gt; I&#39;m new here, but have been into paranormal research for 6 years now.
&gt;&gt; I am the type of person that never gets EVP voices with a recorder so
&gt;&gt; I thought I would experiment with things like the Frank&#39;s box and
&gt;&gt; Ovilus. I recently got the ovilus and brought it to a cemetery and
&gt;&gt; field where a church burned down many years ago. I can not get too
&gt;&gt; specific without having people thinking I am making stuff up but it
&gt;&gt; got fairly wild towards the end of the session. For most of the time
&gt;&gt; we were there the Ovilus seemed to be spitting out a lot of random
&gt;&gt; stuff but it kept mentioning the name Seth. After we moved over to the
&gt;&gt; field where the church was, the ovilus got a lot more active and
&gt;&gt; started saying relevant words like cross and priest. The Ovilus was
&gt;&gt; MUCH more active when being used by our female member. Towards the end
&gt;&gt; the Ovilus said I am Seth, and the woman that was with me told Seth
&gt;&gt; that she did not want to talk to you I&#39;ve heard bad things about you.
&gt;&gt; After that the Ovilus said rather nasty things to her and she started
&gt;&gt; feeling nauseous and she ripped the headphones off her head. Needless
&gt;&gt; to say we ended the session and got out of there.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Over the course of our investigation we found that the Ovilus was
&gt;&gt; saying many words that are not on the 500 word list, so yesterday I
&gt;&gt; did some test recordings to see what words would come up and one of
&gt;&gt; the first things that came up was: seth blamed rest I am not
&gt;&gt; gare demon (all in that order). Needless to say this has me
&gt;&gt; concerned that whatever seth is is still with the box so I am not even
&gt;&gt; storing this thing inside of my house. I have an MP3 of the ovilus
&gt;&gt; saying this.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Also from my experience about 50% of the words it is saying aren&#39;t on
&gt;&gt; the list. Chris Fleming has been getting words not on the list, and
&gt;&gt; Barry FitzGerald has stated that just over 50% of the words he is
&gt;&gt; getting are not on the list. Is there really a much larger list than
&gt;&gt; advertised or is this thing really magic? Highly doubtful IMO.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; My most important question is is anyone else getting the name Seth out
&gt;&gt; of the Ovilus? How many people use this device here?
